    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade FD3S RX-7, showcasing a meticulously preserved 13B-REW power plant with factory-spec compression. This example retains its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, delivering linear boost across the rev range without the typical vacuum-line degradation. The chassis remains structurally flawless, featuring the original aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen LSD that ensures razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in its factory hue with zero orange peel or clear coat failure, the interior exhibits no bolster wear or dash warping. This is a rare, unmolested specimen with perfect synchros and a crisp shifter feel, representing the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering.",
